dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Nattrass Valley quadrangle, Monterey County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Nattrass Valley CA 1967. Photorevised 1984. DMA 1856 III NW, series V895." "First printing, April 2007." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1969. Includes "pertinent references", most recent 1979.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
